[SN]TITLE[SN]
Woman knocked down by van in Glasgow city centre

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman has been knocked down by a van in Glasgow city centre.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The emergency services responded to reports of an incident on West Campbell Street at about 08:45.
The woman was taken to Glasgow Royal Infirmary to be treated for minor injuries.
Police closed the road while investigations were carried out.
